<h2 id="including-via-a-cdn">Including via a CDN</h2>

<p>PDF.js is hosted on several free CDNs:</p>
<ul>
  <li>https://www.jsdelivr.com/package/npm/pdfjs-dist</li>
  <li>https://cdnjs.com/libraries/pdf.js</li>
  <li>https://unpkg.com/pdfjs-dist/</li>
</ul>

