<h2 id="trying-the-viewer">Trying the Viewer</h2>

<p>With the prebuilt or source version, open <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">web/viewer.html</code> in a browser and the test pdf should load. Note: the worker is not enabled for file:// urls, so use a server. If youâ€™re using the source build and have node, you can run <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">gulp server</code>.</p>

<h2 id="more-information">More Information</h2>

<p>For a further walkthrough of a minimal viewer, see the hello world example. More documentation can be found in our <a href="https://github.com/mozilla/pdf.js/wiki">wiki</a> too.</p>
